accessibility.text: I don’t know where to start. I want to start improving my score
My score only updates once a month, on Equifax
I know credit is important, I want to know more
It’s inconvenient to be  on top of my score
How can Vancity help me build credit?
Revise JF. & include on each prototype slide?
This is overwhelming and time consuming
I don’t understand why credit is important
Information about credit is scattered across the Vancity website
